bilingual.target: 老麦克唐纳有一个农场。

list.abstract: Farm，原意指农场，农田，引申义指像勤恳的农民一样，重复的做一件事，通俗的翻译，就是“刷”。另在魔兽RPGdota、LOL等游戏中，farm有打钱的意思，与其相对的是"gank"。

yingyinNormal.en: Can we discuss Yew Tree Farm? What about it?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们能说说紫杉农场吗？怎么了？

yingyinNormal.en: King's Barrow is a working farm. There isn't a spare farmyard half as accessible as here.
yingyinNormal.zh: 金斯巴罗农场在运作，没有更近的闲置农场了。

yingyinNormal.en: Thank you. Do you have far to go? I'm staying at Yew Tree Farm.
yingyinNormal.zh: 谢谢您。你住哪？紫杉农场。

yingyinNormal.en: The only reason he was there was to try to save our farm.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他出现在那里仅仅是为了挽救我们的农场。

yingyinNormal.en: You want to take them to the Drewes' farm? You can come with us if you like.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你想带他们去德鲁家的农场吗？你想来也可以啊。

yingyinNormal.en: It's a pity it should be Yew Tree. It would've filled a hole in the land we farm.
yingyinNormal.zh: 只可惜了紫杉农场，本来刚好可以填补我们的耕地。

yingyinNormal.en: All downhill from here, down to the floodplain. Farm at the bottom of the world.
yingyinNormal.zh: 从这往山下走，一直下到平原，最低的地方就是农场。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, you should have just stayed on the carrot farm? It really is too bad, I did like you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你就该呆在胡萝卜农场里，太可惜了，我挺喜欢你的。

yingyinNormal.en: We worked till, I think, I fainted. But we managed to stop the water. We saved the farm.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们一直挖，直到我累昏过去，但我们成功挡住了洪水，救了农场。

yingyinNormal.en: Marie Audet is a second-generation dairy farmer who doesn't let anything go to waste on her farm.
yingyinNormal.zh: 玛丽·奥迪特是第二代奶农，她不允许她的农场有任何浪费。

yingyinNormal.en: Maybe I should take a page out of Barton's book. Build Pepper a farm, hope nobody blows it up.
yingyinNormal.zh: 或许我向巴顿学习一下，给佩珀建个农场，但愿没人想炸翻它。

yingyinNormal.en: The system cost Marie and her farm over $1 million, which they've paid off in just seven years.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这个系统花了玛丽和她的农场100多万美元，他们在七年内就还清了。

yingyinNormal.en: First, it made things perfect. Then it decided to see what happens if you shake the ant farm.
yingyinNormal.zh: 首先，一切都设计地完美无缺，然后决定试试，摇晃蚂蚁农场，观察反应。

yingyinNormal.en: What you've got in the weapon there, those are blueberries, from my family's farm. They are delicious. You should try some.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你武器里的是我家里农场种的蓝莓，可好吃了，你该尝尝。

yingyinNormal.en: Right. I'm going now. I'll be at my farm if you need me. And take care of that Committee issue.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好吧，我要走了，如果有事，去我的农场找我。还有搞定那个委员会的事情。

yingyinNormal.en: Hey, guys. Hi! How are you? Hi. Where are Cam and Lily? They're still at the farm. I got banished.
yingyinNormal.zh: 大家好。你怎么样？小卡和莉莉在哪里？他们还在农场，我被驱逐出场了。

yingyinNormal.en: And then when they get old, they'll go to that special farm that Chandler took the other chick and duck to.
yingyinNormal.zh: 以后要是老了的话，钱德可以和上次一样把它们送到上次那个农场去。

yingyinNormal.en: So Mr Drewe's accepted your offer. I'm so pleased. The Drewes have been at Yew Tree Farm for many years.
yingyinNormal.zh: 德鲁先生接受你们的提议喽。我太开心了，德鲁家在紫杉农场工作了许多年。

yingyinNormal.en: Later that day we found out we blocked the water all right. We sent it upstream. The whole Lang farm washed away.
yingyinNormal.zh: 后来我们发现，我们挡住了洪水，洪水回流，朗家的整个农场都被冲没了。

yingyinNormal.en: But he would've hated himself even more if he'd lost our farm, if he hadn't been able to provide and support his family.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但如果不能保住我们的农场，他会更痛恨自己，如果他不能养活自己的家人。

examination_example.sentence: Workers won't be returning to the <highlight>farm</highlight>.
The complaints are unlikely to stop without an overhaul of immigration rules for <highlight>farm</highlight> workers.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 如果不彻底改革农场工人的移民规定，这些抱怨不太可能停止。

examination_example.sentence: Perhaps half of U.S. <highlight>farm</highlight> laborers are undocumented immigrants.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 也许一半的美国农场工人是非法移民。

examination_example.sentence: Half of the students in four large philosophy classes read an article on the ethics of factory-<highlight>farmed</highlight> meat.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在四门大型哲学课上，一半的学生阅读了一篇关于工厂化养殖肉类伦理的文章。

examination_example.sentence: To become much more self-sufficient, the UK would need to drastically reduce its consumption of animal foods, and probably also <highlight>farm</highlight> more intensively.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 为了更加自给自足，英国需要大幅减少动物食品的消费，可能还需要更密集地耕种。

examination_example.sentence: Some ants <highlight>farm</highlight> the bugs called aphids for the honeydew they produce when they feed.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 有些蚂蚁养殖那种名为蚜虫的虫子，只是为了得到它们在觅食时产生的蜜汁。
